{"tid":1507101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(法國) 黃背心淪為「為反而反」, 勾結左膠去攪鳩G7","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:47:57.000Z","uid":134071,"like":16,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"52e0a32c7281be2d1f3e9d55017fab909a545129","tid":1507101,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"黃背心自在法國選舉慘敗後, 參與人數人幅減少, 而餘下參與者都失去目標....<br />\n<br />\n而家, 黃背心竟然走去勾結一班反資本主義既左膠, 去攪鳩Donald Trump有份參與既G7.... 已經完全淪為「為反而反」, 為勇武而勇武....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7390947/Yellow-vests-anti-capitalists-blasted-tear-gas-storm-G7-Biarritz.html?ito=1490&amp;ns_campaign=1490&amp;ns_mchannel=rss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-7390947%2FYellow-vests-anti-capitalists-blasted-tear-gas-storm-G7-Biarritz.html%3Fito%3D1490%26ns_campaign%3D1490%26ns_mchannel%3Drss&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=54e23fd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7390947/Yellow-vests-anti-capitalists-blasted-tear-gas-storm-G7-Biarritz.html?ito=1490&amp;ns_campaign=1490&amp;ns_mchannel=rss</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Yellow vests and anti-capitalists join forces to storm the G7</strong> in Biarritz and are blasted with water cannons and tear gas in violent scenes<br />\n<br />\nBy Bridie Pearson-jones and Bryony Jewell and Afp<br />\nPublished: 19:49 BST, 24 August 2019 | Updated: 01:12 BST, 25 August 2019 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>French riot police used water cannons and tear gas on Saturday to disperse anti-capitalism protesters in Bayonne, near the resort of Biarritz where President Emmanuel Macron and G7 nation allies were meeting for a three-day summit. <br />\n<br />\nThousands of anti-globalisation activists, Basque separatists and 'yellow vest' protesters walked from the French town of Hendaye to Irun in Spain, waving banners calling for climate action, gay rights and a fairer economic model.    </strong><br />\n<br />\nA police helicopter circled as dozens of protesters, some hurling stones, shouted slogans and abuse at the lines of police in the Basque town's historic centre.<br />\n<br />\nThe protesters shouted 'Everybody hates the police' and 'anti, anti anti-capitalists' as the mood took a darker turn from peaceful protests earlier in the day in an authorised march on the French-Spanish border.  <br />\n<br />\nA few protesters threw rocks at police, but the crowd in Bayonne was largely peaceful, with some activists dancing. Police responded with warning shots and then water cannon. <br />\n<br />\nThe incident took place near a bridge barricaded by police as part of extensive security measures around the G7 summit meeting in Biarritz that opens Saturday.<br />\n<br />\nEarlier in the day thousands of demonstrators marched peacefully from the area to the Spanish border to demand more action against climate change and economic inequality.        <br />\n<br />\nRoiled by months of anti-government protests this year, France has deployed more than 13,000 police to ensure protesters get nowhere near US President Donald Trump and other leaders. <br />\n<br />\nAuthorities designated two counter-summit 'villages' and the morning protest about 19 miles from the summit. <br />\n<br />\n'The top capitalist leaders are here and we have to show them that the fight continues,' said Alain Missana, 48, an electrician wearing a yellow vest - symbol of the anti-government demonstrations that have been held in France for months.<br />\n<br />\n'It's more money for the rich and nothing for the poor. We see the Amazonian forests burning and the Arctic melting. The leaders will hear us,' he said.<br />\n<br />\nFour police officers were lightly wounded on Friday after protesters fired a homemade mortar near the anti-G7 gathering in Hendaye. <br />\n<br />\nPolice arrested 17 people for hiding their faces.<br />\n..............."},{"pid":"b7d60b3740ded0cadef9d1e271e4474265e11666","tid":1507101,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"(法國) 黃背心運動由贏變輸，抗爭者內訌，選舉慘敗<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1306103/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1306103/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"352dc6ef7292303d923a26728924aedf0ff4a31e","tid":1507101,"uid":134071,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"全世界抗爭者要引以為鑑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963b9417e0df4aff1987bf60220a6da9edbbb591","tid":1507101,"uid":243914,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n核彈都唔割呀"},{"pid":"8148d4e2c36039aca9dc7c11fc769a543fe9e4a6","tid":1507101,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7aDXx3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7aDXx3V.jpg&h=d8b32aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=7860c40c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjbVjJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjbVjJ3.jpg&h=4677b5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=7860c40c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"ad314c1207394a01586ce0d1a86019bbcf526d30","tid":1507101,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=